Abductors of a popular pastor in Akwa Ibom State, Apostle John Okoriko, have demanded the sum of N100million ransom before he could be released from their captivity. Okoriko, who is the Founder and President of Solid Rock Kingdom Church, was reportedly kidnapped on Tuesday night at his church premises in Ibekwe Akpan Nya in Mkpat Enin local government area. It was gathered the hoodlums jumped through the fence and forced their way into the clericâ€™s living room.